OpenHRI office_bot

This repository contains `office_bot`, the reference office-robot project within
OpenHRI.

Source code, documentation, helper scripts, and configuration authored for this
repository are distributed under the Apache License 2.0. See LICENSE.

The repository also includes bundled Gazebo/Ignition simulation world assets
under dev_ws/src/office_bot_model/models/worlds/office_world/. Those model,
mesh, texture, animation, material, and shared media files carry third-party
authorship metadata where available and are not relicensed by the Apache-2.0
project license.

Before reusing, redistributing, or repackaging those simulation assets outside
this repository, review the local metadata and the current attribution status in
docs/asset-attribution.md.
